pageContext.description: Edge sharp but one corner broken off. Loop is missing. One side of socket rim is broken - the pieces are loose inside the socket. A little mud adheres within and at the side of socket. A small hole on one side.
pageContext.patina: dark green grey. showing metal of deep brown where rubbed.
